OL,5, A 13-year-old boy was surrounded by    
OL,6, armed police after an officer mistook  
OL,7, his water pistol for a real gun.       
OL,9,FThe child was "rammed" off his bike by 
OL,10,Fa police van and handcuffed as he was  
OL,11,Fconfronted by marksmen in Hackney, east
OL,12,FLondon, in July, the Alliance for      
OL,13,FPolice Accountability (APA) said.      
OL,15,FIt condemned the response and said the 
OL,16,Fpistol was unmistakably a toy.         
OL,18,FThe Met Police's Det Ch Supt James     
OL,19,FConway said he had apologised for the  
OL,20,F"trauma" caused to the boy.            
